## Additional Terms for Forensic Use

This software is intended for legitimate forensic investigation and data recovery 
purposes only. Users are responsible for:

1. Ensuring proper legal authorization before accessing or analyzing any data
2. Complying with applicable laws and regulations regarding digital forensics
3. Maintaining proper chain of custody for evidence
4. Following established forensic best practices
5. Respecting data privacy and protection requirements

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any misuse of this software
or any legal consequences arising from its use.